<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .button {
            display: block;
            width: 200px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 15px 0;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #888888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome to Our App!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering. Please click the button below to verify your email address and complete your registration.</p>
            <a href="{{url}}" class="button" style="color: #ffffff;">Verify Email</a>
            <p>If you did not create an account, no further action is required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 